{"tid":1579701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐡出軌, 唔通連個天都唔鐘意我?","createTime":"2019-09-18T16:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T16:41:55.000Z","uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1014799e1218d7f017354cd6f3f660d4ad6797e4","tid":1579701,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZoov5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZoov5b.png&h=30a73a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話明出軌, 擺明唔鐘意你啦, 你斑港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲搭黨鐡, 唔單止係過閘, 係擺搭<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我講多次, 係擺搭</span></strong></span><br />\n黨鐡出名咁專一又咁安全,出軌呢D野佢識條鐡咩?<br />\n揾到份文件證明9月16號晚個段軌係換過路軌既<br />\n至於出軌同埋16號晚換個的軌有冇關, 係暫時未知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yi8zCMA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYi8zCMA.png&h=99d788a0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而路軌發現有條空隙<br />\n未知是否因為路軌空隙而引致黨鐡出軌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVrmhRc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVrmhRc.png&h=7c41c73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過老早己經有郭同袍預言過<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1173792935743086593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1173792935743086593&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=36a385bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1173792935743086593&h=85570eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1173792935743086593</a><br />\n黨鐡, 我勸你早日回頭是岸, 呢頂緑帽子港G戴不過<br />\n結局係會同你攬抄<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">願榮耀歸香港</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港, 時代革命</span></span></strong>"}]}